{"tid":2256241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青：六十年代托派「我也曾經勇武過」","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T08:30:52.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a91ae44adf62b74a10c68f5a0a0bfbc19410bf04","tid":2256241,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n施永青是香港藍營富商當中少數不斷寫文章的 thinker，雖然我們對香港前途、社會運動的立場不同，但他的人生經驗，無疑是很有趣的對話對象。施永青自言年輕時是一個「托派」，也曾經相當勇武，回想那段日子，他覺得對日後從商的鍛鍊有不少幫助；而談及當年戰友，他認為長毛加入議會並不符合「托派」理想，反而自己雖然變成有錢人，但一直提倡「三三三制」，卻更能令社會資源有效再分配。無論是否認同他的理論，他的自白，很有助我們了解整套藍營論述的內心世界。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=EiHrKVBgpXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEiHrKVBgpXg&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=fae1630f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=EiHrKVBgpXg</a>"},{"pid":"00185d29122e113a8b96675c1f3011f3460a7dc1","tid":2256241,"uid":295230,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦，當時你只係個極左on9仔信啲用個諗下都知無可能既社會體制"},{"pid":"93ca68b21b4b96ee3bd214f704464d16afd46c8f","tid":2256241,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />施永廢青 死暴徒"},{"pid":"fc0a37949d508624ff9b3281cf49e283bbb116cb","tid":2256241,"uid":292987,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"托派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />托柒派就有你份"},{"pid":"21f4601178d74af1a3b9bc66d06349a79b4eb5a0","tid":2256241,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75b0f307c688ca76774d9b1314dc56c98edc4b1","tid":2256241,"uid":289292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"湯11都曾經係泛民"},{"pid":"ec